B.aLv=new A.dJ("Techstep was a subgenre of drum and bass popular in the late 90s. Characterized by dark synths and sci-fi tones, in its hay-day, Techstep was in fact the leading sound of DnB. The subgenre started to loose traction around the start of the new millennium and later matured into Neofunk. Here is a mix comprising of my favorite tracks over the subgenre's first four and most influential years.","techstep-1995-1999","Techstep 1995 - 1998","2015-10-08",B.an)
